The current `int_buf` module is fork of the
[`itoa`](https://crates.io/crates/itoa/1.0.9) crate.

It includes the following changes:
- rename `Integer` to `IntBufAble`.
- rename `Buffer` to `IntBuf`.
	- divide fn `write` into `write_bytes` and `write_str`.
	- rename fn `format` to `to_str`.
	- new fn `to_bytes`.
- update docs and examples.
- remove `no_panic`.
- refactorize.
